<div class="sidebarLeftData">
	<div class="img"><img src="css/img/section/wbut.png"></div>
	<h2>West Bengal University of Technology</h2>
	<h3>A Brief History</h3>
	<p>The West Bengal University of Technology came into existence on August 5, 2000. The University in-house department first started as IIIT-C. Later on, with the need of the industry and policies taken by State Government, for a higher quality engineering and technology education, School of Engineering and Technology - WBUT was formed along with School of Biotechnology &amp Biological Sciences, School of Management &amp Natural Sciences. 
The University which began its operation only with 30 colleges, now has strength of 217 colleges. The increase of Post Graduate courses and R&ampD activity has provided the University an edge advantage and helped the education arena to meet the gap of future Human Resource in Education. The University is continuously and effortlessly busy in up gradation of Education in West Bengal with the help of UGC, AICTE and State Government.
In the last decade, WBUT being a Centre of Excellence for higher studies and research, engaged in National Building Exercise. The basic objective of the University is to organize undergraduate and post graduate courses of study in Engineering, Technology & Management, also in emerging areas with a view to produce young scientists, technologists and managers of high caliber, capable of contributing towards development of the country.</p>
